Consider the following C program segment:

#include <stdio.h>
int main() {
    char s1[7] = "1234", *p;
    p = s1 + 2;
    *p = '0';
    printf("%s", s1);
}

What will be printed by the program?
A. 12
B. 120000
C. 1204
D. 1034

